# CloudDrive

A modern, user-friendly OneDrive client for Linux.

## Sample Configuration

```toml
log_level = "INFO"
minimize_to_tray = true
autostart = true

[sync]
sync_dir = "~/OneDrive"
sync_interval_seconds = 300

[auth]
client_id = "your-client-id-here"

[notifications]
enabled = true
```

See `~/.config/clouddrive/config.toml` for full options.
